      <container name="Recalling" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling</span> its resolution <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/73/258">73/258</a> of 20 December 2018 on cooperation between the United Nations and the Organisation for the Prohibition of Chemical Weapons,</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Having received" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Having received</span> the annual report for 2018 and the draft report for 2019 of the Organisation for the Prohibition of Chemical Weapons on the implementation of the Convention on the Prohibition of the Development, Production, Stockpiling and Use of Chemical Weapons and on Their Destruction,<authorialNote marker="1" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_1"><p xml:space="preserve">		See <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/75/128">A/75/128</a>.</p></authorialNote></p>
